014package org.gbif.api.model.collections.request;
015
016import java.util.List;
017import java.util.UUID;
018import javax.annotation.Nullable;
019import lombok.Data;
020import lombok.EqualsAndHashCode;
021import lombok.experimental.SuperBuilder;
022
023@EqualsAndHashCode(callSuper = true)
024@SuperBuilder
025@Data
026public class CollectionSearchRequest extends SearchRequest {
027
028  @Deprecated @Nullable private List<UUID> institution;
029  @Nullable private List<String> contentTypes;
030  @Nullable private List<String> preservationTypes;
031  @Nullable private List<String> accessionStatus;
032  @Nullable private List<Boolean> personalCollection;
033}
